OL,3,CEuropean ambassadors say international
OL,4,Cschools in UK should avoid VAT levy
OL,6,FEuropean ambassadors have warned that
OL,7,Fimposing VAT on international schools
OL,8,Fin the UK could lead to hundreds of
OL,9,Fpupils leaving.
OL,11,FGerman ambassador Miguel Berger and
OL,12,FFrench ambassador Helene Duchene told
OL,13,FThe Times they wanted international
OL,14,Fschools excluded from plans to impose
OL,15,F20% VAT on private schools.
OL,17,FFrom January, the Government plans to
OL,18,Fremove the VAT exemption and business
OL,19,Frates relief for private schools to
OL,20,Fenable funding for 6,500 new teachers
OL,21,Fin state schools.
