OL,3,CEuropean ambassadors say international
OL,4,Cschools in UK should avoid VAT levy
OL,6,FMr Berger said executives of companies
OL,7,Fthat invest in the UK "must know they
OL,8,Fcan send their children to a German
OL,9,Fschool".
OL,11,FCritics of the VAT change have warned
OL,12,Fabout the short timescale involved and
OL,13,Fthe risk of unintended consequences,
OL,14,Fincluding the impact on children with
OL,15,Flearning difficulties who attend
OL,16,Fspecialist independent schools and
OL,17,Fmilitary families.
OL,19,FThere are 11 schools accredited by the
OL,20,FFrench Ministry for Education in the
OL,21,FUK, nine of which are in London.
