OL,3,CEuropean ambassadors say international
OL,4,Cschools in UK should avoid VAT levy
OL,6,FMs Duchene said these schools would be
OL,7,F"weakened" by the VAT change.
OL,9,FShe added: "We are not asking for an
OL,10,Fexemption: we are not the target of
OL,11,Fthis VAT measure.
OL,13,F"Our schools are different from the
OL,14,Ftarget ones since we follow special
OL,15,Fcourses preparing for French exams.
OL,17,F"These parents don't have a plan B
OL,18,Fbecause other schools don't follow the
OL,19,FFrench curriculum."
